		</div><!-- end vocab -->	
		
		
   		<!-- HOW CONTENT -->
    	<div class="titlebar to_how">How do I use Curarium?</div>
		<div>		
				<table class="howitem" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr valign="top">
					<td><%= image_tag "hint_collection.png", id: "hint_coll" %></td>
					<td>Collect<ol>
					<li>Find and follow <span class="vcoll">collections</span> of interest to you </li>
					<li>OR <span class="ving">ingest</span> your own <span class="vcoll">collection</span>* of up to 30,000 <span class="vrec">records</span> in just 5 minutes. *Requires JSON files and offsite hosting</li>
					</ol></td>
				</tr></table>
				<table class="howitem" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr valign="top">
					<td><%= image_tag "hint_explore.png", id: "hint_coll" %></td>
					<td>Explore<ol>
				<li>Within any <span class="vcoll">collection</span>, browse, filter, search, and generate visualizations.</li>
				<li><span class="vann">Annotate</span> <span class="vrec">records</span> and make additions to their metadata.</li>
				<li>Save individual <span class="vrec">records</span>, groups of <span class="vrec">records</span>, or visualizations to a <span class="vtra">tray</span>. </li>
				<li>Categorize what you save using as many <span class="vtra">trays</span> as you need.</li>
				</ol></td>
				</tr></table>
				<table class="howitem" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr valign="top">
					<td><%= image_tag "hint_spotlight.png", id: "hint_coll" %></td>
					<td><span class="vspo">Spotlight</span><ol>
				<li>Tell stories by pulling directly from the content you’ve collected in your <span class="vtra">trays</span>.</li>
				<li>Publish, share, and export your <span class="vspo">spotlights</span>.</li>
				</ol></td>
				</tr></table>
				<table class="howitem" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr valign="top">
					<td><%= image_tag "hint_user.png", id: "hint_coll" %></td>
					<td>User<ol>
				<li>Edit your <span class="vcoll">collections</span>, <span class="vtra">trays</span>, and <span class="vspo">spotlights</span>.</li>
				<li>Track <span class="vcoll">collections</span> and users you follow.</li>
				<li>Start or join user <span class="vcir">circles</span> to share and collaborate on work within a specified <span class="vcoll">collection</span> or set of <span class="vcoll">collections</span>.</li>
				<li>From your <span class="vcir">circle’s</span> splash page, access <span class="vcir">circle</span>-specific <span class="vcoll">collections</span>; check the newsfeed to find updated <span class="vcir">circle</span> annotations, <span class="vstra">social trays</span>, and <span class="vspo">spotlights</span>; post comments to your <span class="vcir">circle</span> members.</li>
				<li>When you explore any <span class="vcoll">collections</span> in your <span class="vcir">circles</span>, you can use a <span class="vstra">social tray</span> to work in real time with <span class="vcir">circle</span> members to collect and order <span class="vrec">records</span>.</li>
				</ol></td>
				</tr></table>        
		</div><!-- end how -->
		
		
